notesStmt.note: This workshop discussion is on the European youth pact and the job situation of young people in Europe. The participants are representatives of different European youth organizations. They present the outcomes of what they discussed in small sub-groups before this event. They know each other from previous discussions, the atmosphere is relaxed and friendly.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
